					<li>
						<a
							href="http://wiki.eclipse.org/EclipseLink/UserGuide/JPA/Advanced_JPA_Development/Performance/Performance_Monitoring_and_Profiling/Performance_Monitoring">New Performance Monitor</a>
					</li>
